                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <colophon xml:id="coloph2">
                  <locus target="#267r" facs="271">Fol. 267r</locus>
                  <q>“Here ends the book of Esther on the 10th of Mäggabit, 1963 EC [= 19 March 1971]. May God forgive Gäbrä Maryam and Nǝburä ‘Ǝdǝ Dǝmeṭǝros, whose baptismal name is Kinä Śǝlassie.”</q>
                  Hereafter, the names of his children are listed
                </colophon>


                  </msItem>
